{"tid":1725163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前線巴絲請珍惜裝備","createTime":"2019-11-15T16:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T16:25:28.000Z","uid":269641,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"83d77f1367a056c12895d4acfb40965a66847cde","tid":1725163,"uid":269641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"我唔知前線仲有無睇連登 <br />\n<br />\n我係一個係外國提供玩具的家長。<br />\n由8 月開始一路安排 D 玩具返香港。<br />\n我最近聽到好多出去的仔女已經習慣有野攞， 就好容易棄置唔要D gear。當然比狗查就真係唔好搏。我想你地知道D gear 就算係外國都已經越來越難搵同買。你地如果能夠recycle 就最好。老實講，真係唔知幾時唔比入境。請用得就用！ <br />\n<br />\n因為你多攞一個你唔需要的gear, 我地就幫少個手足，唔該曬！！！"},{"pid":"a89d7a6e208c0b9f3f8eb3d2de6a7f81db211204","tid":1725163,"uid":269641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211a1a8def17ecd9f8464d0f4386d896a524ecef","tid":1725163,"uid":269641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e918dda26923f2e570e46e3d5c2ead57301a737f","tid":1725163,"uid":287064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:17:04.000Z","msg":"其實應該盡量收係啲隱蔽位，第日安全情況下返黎拎返"},{"pid":"5278301aca69a2aeb0e1af8169a5d2d82274fdb2","tid":1725163,"uid":237495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:25:28.000Z","msg":"push"}]}